\left\{\forall_{x, y \in \left(\mathbb{C}^{2}\right)^{\otimes n}}~\left(\hspace{2em} \Qcircuit@C=1em @R=.7em{
& \lstick{a} & \gate{u} & \control \qw \qwx[1] & \rstick{b} \qw   \\ 
  & \lstick{x} & { /^{n} } \qw & \gate{U} & \rstick{y} \qw 
} \hspace{2em} \Rightarrow \left(\hspace{2em} \Qcircuit@C=1em @R=.7em{
& \lstick{c} & { /^{k} } \qw & \qw & \qw \qwx[1]   \\ 
  & \lstick{a} & \gate{u} & \control \qw \qwx[1] & \qw & { /^{k + 1} } \qw & \rstick{d} \qw   \\ 
  & \lstick{x} & { /^{n} } \qw & \gate{U} & \rstick{y} \qw 
} \hspace{2em} \Rightarrow \left(d = \left(c {\otimes} b\right)\right)\right)\right) \textrm{ if } d \in \left(\mathbb{C}^{2}\right)^{\otimes \left(k + 1\right)}\right..